# ── Build artifacts ──
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# ── IDE / Editor ──
**/.vs/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.sln.docstates

# ── Dependencies ──
**/node_modules/

# ── Version control ──
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitmodules

# ── Environment / Secrets ──
**/.env
**/.env.*

# ── Test output ──
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/coverage-final/
**/coveragereport/

# ── Logs / Backups ──
**/Logs/
**/Backups/

# ── Documentation (not needed in image) ──
**/Docs/
*.md

# ── Scripts / Installer (not needed in image) ──
**/Scripts/
**/Installer/

# ── Docker files (prevent recursive COPY) ──
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

# ── CI/CD ──
**/.github/
**/.gitlab-ci.yml

# ── Frontend (not needed for WebAPI image) ──
**/frontend/
**/wwwroot/

# ── Misc ──
**/*.md
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
